wishlist
========

wishlist is a small application that fetches book prices from a variety of
sources simultaneously.


* Requirements

- Ruby (1.8)

- hpricot (0.8.4)
  gem install hpricot --source http://gemcutter.org

- schleyfox-peach (0.3)
  gem install schleyfox-peach --source=http://gems.github.com


* Usage

./wishlist <amazon wishlist URL>

To experiment with my wishlist:

./wishlist  "http://www.amazon.co.uk/registry/wishlist/LZFWWJ0ZZGYC/ref=cm_wl_act_vv?_encoding=UTF8&visitor-view=1&reveal="

